Well where to start first off thanks Relizlab for one nice video and CARS.2.iPhoneCAM-FU for some pretty good audio THANKS. Ok on my part i used the Russain video and split it up into a whole bunch of splits synced each peice and joined then and it came out damn good bout as good as it gets i think. Now my encode i did alot to just because well cuz i can. 



I adjusted chroma saturation and the regular stuff but i did indeed use a few custom filters i had made from prior encodes so it worked i noticed there is a red overlay in most of the encodes ive saw so i went ahead and corrected it the way i feel it should look.
